data.description: FALL in love with this adorable 2 bedroom 1 bathroom updated home!  This home has tons of storage! It has a walk-in pantry & walk-in closets. Don't forget it comes with a fenced-in yard, a newer roof, a new sewer line,  windows with a lifetime warranty, quartz countertops, a farmhouse sink, a hands-free faucet, bar seating for 4, and bamboo floors.  Also, this home is enrolled in Miami County's 10-year tax abatement program which will save the new owner money on their property taxes!
